<paragraph pageId="45" pageNumber="46">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="45" pageNumber="46">
Five species have been described. These usually display different colour varieties. Two species from Madagascar, previously included in the genus 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Blepharida" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Blepharida" order="Coleoptera" pageId="45" pageNumber="46" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Blepharida</taxonomicName>
